## рҹ“Ң What is CivicConnect?

CivicConnect is a full-stack **MERN** application where registered citizens can report local civic problems вҖ” potholes, broken streetlights, overflowing drains вҖ” and rally community support through upvoting.

The more upvotes an issue collects, the higher its priority climbs **automatically**. If the responsible authority doesn't act within a configurable time window, the issue **auto-escalates** up a 3-tier admin hierarchy (Ward вҶ’ District вҶ’ City), so no complaint ever gets buried.

### Why it's different from a standard complaint form

| Traditional Systems | CivicConnect |
|---------------------|-------------|
| Submit and wait forever | Real-time status tracking |
| No community input | Upvote system surfaces urgent issues |
| Single point of failure | 3-tier authority chain with auto-escalation |
| Anonymous, unverified reports | Verified citizen accounts |
| No accountability | Full public audit trail |

