## вңЁ Features

### рҹ‘Ө For Citizens

- рҹ”җ **Verified registration** вҖ” ward/district stored at signup to route reports to the right authority automatically
- рҹ“Қ **Rich issue reports** вҖ” title, description, 15 categories, text address, interactive map pin, photo/video uploads
- рҹ‘Қ **Community upvoting** вҖ” upvote issues you care about (cannot upvote your own)
- рҹ“Ҡ **Automatic priority upgrade via upvotes**

  | Upvotes | Priority |
  |---------|----------|
  | 0вҖ“9 | рҹ”ө Low |
  | 10вҖ“24 | рҹҹЎ Medium |
  | 25вҖ“49 | рҹ”ҙ High |
  | 50+ | рҹҹЈ Critical |

- рҹ“Ҳ **Live progress bar** on every issue card showing votes needed for the next priority level
- рҹ”ә **Escalation trail** вҖ” full history of when and why an issue moved up the chain
- рҹ—әпёҸ **Interactive map** вҖ” all issues pinned with colour-coded status markers
- рҹ”Ҙ **Sort modes** вҖ” Hot (by upvotes) В· New (by date) В· Critical (by priority)
- рҹ”Қ **Filter panel** вҖ” by category, status, and priority simultaneously

### рҹӣЎпёҸ For Admins вҖ” 3-Tier Hierarchy

| Level | Role | Jurisdiction | Extra Privileges |
|-------|------|-------------|-----------------|
| **L1** | Ward Admin | Issues in their ward | вҖ” |
| **L2** | District Admin | L1 + L2 issues | Promote users to L1, delete issues |
| **L3** | City Admin | All issues | Promote anyone, full control |

- рҹҺҡпёҸ **Scoped dashboard** вҖ” each admin only sees issues within their jurisdiction
- вң… **Status management** вҖ” Pending вҶ’ In Progress вҶ’ Resolved вҶ’ Escalated
- рҹ”§ **Issue assignment** вҖ” assign to a specific admin at the correct level
- рҹ”ә **Manual escalation** вҖ” push an issue up with a written reason
- вҸұпёҸ **Automatic idle escalation** вҖ” cron runs every 60 min; issues that exceed their idle threshold escalate automatically
- рҹ’¬ **Internal comments** вҖ” admins add updates that are visible to citizens
- рҹ‘Ҙ **Team management** вҖ” promote/demote users directly from the admin dashboard
- рҹ“Ҡ **Live stats strip** вҖ” Total / Pending / In Progress / Escalated / Resolved / Critical

### рҹҸ·пёҸ 15 Issue Categories

| | | |
|---|---|---|
| рҹ—‘пёҸ Garbage & Sanitation | рҹ’Ў Street Lighting | рҹӣЈпёҸ Roads & Potholes |
| рҹ’§ Water Supply | рҹҡ° Sewage & Drainage | рҹҢі Parks & Public Spaces |
| рҹ”Ҡ Noise Pollution | рҹҢ«пёҸ Air Pollution | рҹҗ• Stray Animals |
| рҹҸ—пёҸ Illegal Construction | вҡЎ Electricity | рҹҡҢ Public Transport |
| рҹҡҰ Traffic & Signals | рҹҢҝ Trees & Encroachment | рҹ“Ң Other |

