## рҹӣ пёҸ Tech Stack

### Frontend

| Technology | Version | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|---------|
| React | 19 | UI framework |
| Vite | 5 | Build tool + dev server with `/api` proxy |
| React Router | v6 | Client-side routing |
| Framer Motion | 11 | Animations |
| Leaflet + React-Leaflet | 1.9 / 5 | Interactive maps |
| Context API | вҖ” | Global state (`AuthContext`, `IssueContext`) |
| Vercel | вҖ” | Hosting + CDN |

### Backend

| Technology | Version | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|---------|
| Node.js | 18+ | Runtime |
| Express | 4.18 | REST API framework |
| MongoDB Atlas | вҖ” | Database |
| Mongoose | 8 | ODM |
| bcryptjs | 2.4 | Password hashing |
| jsonwebtoken | 9 | JWT auth |
| setInterval | вҖ” | Auto-escalation cron job |
| Render | вҖ” | Hosting |

### Architecture Pattern

```
Frontend (MVC-inspired)
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ pages/          вҶҗ Controllers  (smart, read context, call hooks)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ components/     вҶҗ Views        (pure UI вҖ” props in, JSX out, zero API calls)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ context/        вҶҗ Global state (AuthContext, IssueContext)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ hooks/          вҶҗ Logic        (useIssueForm)
в””в”Җв”Җ services/api.js вҶҗ Model        (every single fetch() call lives here)
```

