## рҹ—әпёҸ API Reference

### Auth вҖ” `/api/auth`

| Method | Endpoint | Auth Required | Description |
|--------|----------|--------------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/register` | None | Create citizen account |
| `POST` | `/login` | None | Returns JWT token + user object |
| `GET` | `/me` | рҹ”’ Any user | Get current user profile |
| `PATCH` | `/promote` | рҹ”‘ L2+ Admin | Promote a user to admin (body: `userId`, `adminLevel`, `ward`, `district`, `city`) |
| `PATCH` | `/demote` | рҹ”‘ L2+ Admin | Demote admin to citizen (body: `userId`) |
| `GET` | `/admins` | рҹ”‘ L1+ Admin | List all admins |

### Issues вҖ” `/api/issues`

| Method | Endpoint | Auth Required | Description |
|--------|----------|--------------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/` | None | All issues with filters + pagination |
| `GET` | `/:id` | None | Single issue with full details |
| `POST` | `/` | рҹ”’ Any user | Create a new issue |
| `PATCH` | `/:id/status` | рҹ”‘ L1+ Admin | Update status + optional comment |
| `PATCH` | `/:id/assign` | рҹ”‘ L1+ Admin | Assign to an admin |
| `PATCH` | `/:id/priority` | рҹ”‘ L1+ Admin | Manually override priority |
| `POST` | `/:id/escalate` | рҹ”‘ L1+ Admin | Manually escalate with reason |
| `POST` | `/:id/upvote` | рҹ”’ Any user | Toggle upvote (auto-upgrades priority at thresholds) |
| `POST` | `/:id/comment` | рҹ”’ Any user | Add a comment |
| `DELETE` | `/:id` | рҹ”‘ L2+ Admin | Delete a single issue |
| `DELETE` | `/` | рҹ”‘ L2+ Admin | Delete all issues |

**Query params for `GET /api/issues`:**

```
?category=Roads & Potholes
&status=Pending
&priority=High
&level=1
&page=1
&limit=20
```

